PRICE REDUCTION! QUICK CLOSE PREFERRED WITH NO CONTINGENCIES. This exceptional smart home defines modern living with 6 bedrooms, 4 baths, and over 3600 sq ft on an 8200 sq ft corner lot. The main level bedroom adds flexibility, and the home theater ensures immersive cinematic enjoyment. The master retreat upstairs includes a cozy seating area and a lavish en-suite bathroom with dual sinks.

The loft area is versatile for a home office, and the finished basement accommodates guests with a bedroom, bath, laundry room, and dry bar. The heart of the home features a fireplace and built-in entertainment center. Outside, an inviting pergola and spa hookups promise year-round relaxation.

Eco-conscious features include a 220V electric car charging outlet in the heated 3-car garage. With fresh interior and exterior paint, this property exemplifies intelligent design, technological advancement, and comfort. Welcome to a lifestyle where modern living is an art, offering a haven that's brilliant in both innovation and style.
